summary: Face and body preset (CME) for Enhanced Character Edit.
descriptionHtml:
[b][font=Verdana][color=#efefef]Alexia Vici - CME Save Data[/color][/font][/b]
[i][color=#bf9000]"Cute and deadly" / "Stealth Assassin"[/color][/i]

[color=#cccccc]I wanted a beautiful-looking character with high[/color]
[color=#cccccc]stealth and assassination abilities, so I created Alexia.[/color]
[color=#cccccc]Best looking with dual "Blade of Woe", having sneak lvl at 100[/color]
[color=#cccccc]with all its perks unlocked and invisibility power.[/color]

[color=#cccccc]What to do? Sneak behind somebody and slit their throat, ending[/color]
[color=#cccccc]their lives with one hit. Unless you're a hardcore motherf....?[/color]

[color=#666666]__________________________________________________________[/color]

[b][font=Verdana][color=#efefef]Required Mods:[/color][/font][/b]
[color=#999999]●[/color] [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12951]Enhanced Character Edit[/url]
[color=#999999]●[/color] [url=http://goo.gl/w6RrLt]SG Hair Pack 268[/url]
[color=#999999]●[/color] [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267]SG Female Textures Renewal[/url]

[b][font=Verdana][color=#efefef]Optional Mods:[/color][/font][/b]
[color=#999999]●[/color] [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/53442]zzjay's Wardrobe[/url]
[color=#999999]●[/color] [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/37900]UNP Blessed Body Redux
[/url]
[color=#666666]__________________________________________________________[/color]

[b][font=Verdana][color=#efefef]Installation:[/color][/font][/b]
[color=#cccccc]Drop the file in[/color] [color=#ffff00][Documents\My Games\Skyrim\CME_save][/color]

[b][font=Verdana][color=#efefef]Uninstallation:[/color][/font][/b]
[color=#cccccc]Remove the file from CME_Save folder.[/color]

[color=#666666]__________________________________________________________[/color]

[b][font=Verdana][color=#efefef]Notes:[/color][/font][/b]
[color=#999999]●[/color][color=#cccccc] When loading the slot, DO NOT select a preset. [/color]
[color=#cccccc]  Simply click "Next" and load it.[/color]

[color=#999999]●[/color][color=#cccccc] You may change the _#_ in the file name to whatever[/color]
[color=#cccccc]  you want depending on the available slot you have.[/color]
author: Sezvek
